{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "A dialog of a FF guarding southern gates of Rivington near the battlefield."
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "12": {
      "id": "12",
      "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
      "text": "Turn back, citizen. No passage in this direction.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [
        "WYR_Rivington_HasMet_FlamingFist_004"
      ],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "15",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "17": {
          "id": "17",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Why not?",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "WYR_Rivington_AskedAboutBattle = False"
          ],
          "setflags": [
            "WYR_Rivington_AskedAboutBattle"
          ],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "15",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "30": {
              "id": "30",
              "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
              "text": "It's bloodier than a butcher's backyard out there. Piles of dead Absolutists, and a few of our own as well.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "15",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {}
            }
          }
        },
        "3": {
          "id": "3",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Don't tell me where I can and can't go.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "5": {
              "id": "5",
              "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
              "text": "It's my job to do exactly that. If you intend to spend any time in Baldur's Gate, you best learn some respect for the Flaming Fist.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "8": {
                  "id": "8",
                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                  "text": "And trust me, you don't want to go out there.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "15": {
                      "id": "15",
                      "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                      "text": "The cultists assaulted the gate, armed to the teeth, trying to break in.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "25": {
                          "id": "25",
                          "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                          "text": "They nearly had it too, before the Steel Watch intervened.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "19": {
                              "id": "19",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I take it the Steel Watch won?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "GLO_SteelWatchers_Knows_AboutSteelWatchers"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "18": {
                                  "id": "18",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "With ease. They could stop a dragon.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "26": {
                              "id": "26",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Those Steel Watchers sure do get around.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "GLO_SteelWatchers_Knows_AboutSteelWatchers"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "10": {
                                  "id": "10",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "You've had the pleasure of meeting one? Then you know the city's in good hands.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "16": {
                              "id": "16",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Thank the gods for the Steel Watch.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "GLO_SteelWatchers_Knows_AboutSteelWatchers"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "9": {
                                  "id": "9",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "Thank Lord Gortash. No doubt we'll be needing them again before too long. You be safe now.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "24": {
                              "id": "24",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Be careful of the Steel Watch. They're not the salvation you think they are.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "GLO_SteelWatchers_Knows_AboutSteelWatchers",
                                "CLERIC"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "29": {
                                  "id": "29",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "Ah, you're one of those.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "1": {
                                      "id": "1",
                                      "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                      "text": "Lord Gortash warned there would be doubters. Where there is genius, there are always sceptics.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "7": {
                                          "id": "7",
                                          "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                          "text": "Luckily for you, the Steel Watchers protect all law-abiding citizens equally.",
                                          "context": "NodeContext: with a touch of superiority",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "11": {
                              "id": "11",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Steel Watch - is that some sort of fancy new rank of city watchman?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "GLO_SteelWatchers_Knows_AboutSteelWatchers = False"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "0": {
                                  "id": "0",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "A little more than that.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "2": {
                                      "id": "2",
                                      "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                      "text": "You'll see for yourself soon enough if you head to the city.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "20": {
                              "id": "20",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Sounds like the battle's over then.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "27": {
                                  "id": "27",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "For now. But I can't let you pass - we might have repelled an advance party, but they'll strike again.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "6": {
                              "id": "6",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I prefer guards with actual faith in what they're protecting.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "GLO_SteelWatchers_Knows_AboutSteelWatchers = False",
                                "CLERIC"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "4": {
                                  "id": "4",
                                  "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                  "text": "Look pal, faith or no, the sooner the Steel Watch replaces me the better.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "22": {
                                      "id": "22",
                                      "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                      "text": "There's no reason for me stick my neck out against armies of cultists when we can send mountains of steel instead.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "28": {
                                          "id": "28",
                                          "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                          "text": "Way I see it, the city's a whole lot safer since the Steel Watch showed up. And we can thank the late Lord Gortash for that.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [
                                            "GLO_Gortash_State_WorldKnowsPermaDefeated"
                                          ],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        },
                                        "14": {
                                          "id": "14",
                                          "speaker": "Fist Osmund",
                                          "text": "Way I see it, city's got a whole lot safer since the Steel Watch showed up. For that, we can thank Lord Gortash.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "21": {
                              "id": "21",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Leave.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
